weddings through the years....

Here is a look at how wedding styles have changed. Some of our couples are incomplete but we understand that the marriages actually did take place. Where applicable in the titles, the groom's surname name is given first and then the bride's. Let us know if you have more wedding pictures for us. All are welcome but we are especially glad to get the old ones because those couples connect to so many people. A bigger picture will pop up if you click on the thumbnail. Then just click on your browser's "back" button to return to this page.
